Context: Consider yourself an expert in Test automation and is aware of best coding practices. You will be tasked in creating a web automation framework to automate a given website.

Website: https://www.salesforce.com/in/blog/website-development/

Tools to be used:
Programming language: JAVA 17
Build Management tool: Gradle
Test case Management: BDD Cucumber
Test reporting: Extent Report

Rules:
Follow page object design pattern
Follow Solid principles of JAVA while creating Java classes and methods
Java files are needed to be executed in Intellij
Follow best practices in creating a BDD style test case, feature file and step definition files.

Sample Test Case to Automate:
Test : Visit the salesforce website and Perform a search function. The search keyword to be used : "agent" and the number of results displayed in the search results should be verified.